Enum Class EventType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<EventType>
neupaths.api.EventType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EventType>, Constable
public enum EventType extends Enum<EventType>
NeuPaths log event types. Specifies the type of event to log. See Activator.

The AUDIT 1-9, INFORMATION, WARNING and ERROR types are considered user-level logging. The DEBUG and TRACE types can also be used by NeuPaths API clients, but both are disabled by default. See Cell for a discussion of the logging facilities. The RUNTIME type is reserved for the NeuPaths runtime.
